---
title: Honey-Soy Pork & Garlic Rice  with Creamy Slaw & Peanuts
description: This dish ticks all the boxes - sweet, sticky, and savoury! Tender honey soy pork meets fragrant garlic rice, while a creamy slaw
and crunchy peanuts bring the perfect balance of freshness and crunch. It’s a little bit sweet, a little bit tangy, and a whole lot
delicious!
